snippet.title: Quantum Paradox Demo 4K Gameplay Video
snippet.description:
Demo version of mod Quantum Paradox - singleplayer Half-life 2 modification from Russian developers team.

The player will have to fight with crowds of zombies, while fighting off soldiers, in almost completely abandoned post-war St. Petersburg.

This demo version is made on the source 1 engine. We switched to using source 2.

Moddb - https://www.moddb.com/mods/quantum-paradox
Группа ВКонтакте - https://vk.com/quantum_paradox
